annotationA: Signal peptidase complex catalytic subunit SEC11; Peptidase activity; serine-type peptidase activity. It is involved in the biological process described with: signal peptide processing
annotationB: Mesencephalic astrocyte-derived neurotrophic factor homolog; Required during the maturation of the embryonic nervous system for maintenance of neuronal and cuticular connectivity. Essential for maintenance of dopaminergic neurons and dopamine levels
